---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - RentGrab"
  description="RentGrab Privacy Policy - Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <div class="container-lg py-12">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="text-neutral-600 space-y-6">
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold">Effective Date: August 2025</p>
          <p class="font-semibold">Last Updated: August 2025</p>
        </div>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Introduction</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Welcome to RentGrab ("we," "our," or "us"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our pre-launch website and sign up for our email list.</p>
          <p>As we are currently in pre-launch phase, this policy specifically covers our email collection and communication practices. We will update this policy before our platform launches to include comprehensive information about our full service.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">Information You Provide</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Email Address:</strong> When you sign up for early access or our waitlist</li>
            <li><strong>Name (optional):</strong> If you choose to provide it</li>
            <li><strong>Feedback:</strong> Any comments or suggestions you send us</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">Information Automatically Collected</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Analytics Data:</strong> We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors interact with our website</li>
            <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Browser type, operating system, and device type</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent on site, and referral source</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="mb-2">We use the information we collect to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>Send you updates about our launch</li>
            <li>Provide early access opportunities</li>
            <li>Share exclusive pre-launch offers</li>
            <li>Respond to your inquiries</li>
            <li>Improve our website and planned services</li>
            <li>Analyze website traffic and user behavior</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Email Communications</h2>
          <p class="mb-2">By joining our waitlist, you agree to receive:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-1">
            <li>Launch announcements</li>
            <li>Product updates and features</li>
            <li>Early bird specials</li>
            <li>Occasional surveys for feedback</li>
          </ul>
          <p>You can unsubscribe at any time by clicking the "unsubscribe" link in any email.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
          <p class="mb-2">We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information. We may share your information only in these circumstances:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>With service providers who help us operate our website (e.g., email service providers)</li>
            <li>If required by law or legal process</li>
            <li>To protect our rights or safety</li>
            <li>With your consent</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Data Security</h2>
          <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="mb-2">You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-1">
            <li>Access the personal information we have about you</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your information</li>
            <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
          </ul>
          <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@rentgrab.com" class="text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-600">info@rentgrab.com</a></p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Cookies</h2>
          <p class="mb-2">Our website uses cookies to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-1">
            <li>Remember your preferences</li>
            <li>Analyze website traffic (Google Analytics)</li>
            <li>Improve user experience</li>
          </ul>
          <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>Our services are not intended for children under 18. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 18.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">International Data Transfers</h2>
          <p>If you access our website from outside the United States, please be aware that your information may be transferred to, stored, and processed in the United States.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="mb-2">If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
          <div class="bg-neutral-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p class="font-semibold">RentGrab</p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@rentgrab.com" class="text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-600">info@rentgrab.com</a></p>
            <p>Website: <a href="https://www.rentgrab.com" class="text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-600">www.rentgrab.com</a></p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 italic">This privacy policy is for our pre-launch phase. A comprehensive privacy policy covering all platform features will be published before our official launch.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Back to Home -->
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-600 font-medium transition-colors">
        <span>‚Üê</span>
        <span>Back to Blog</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>